Package org.reso.resoscript

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.reso.resoscript.Settings
  • public class Settings
extends java.lang.Object
    The settings class contains all the settings a server can have, which currently means the following: * client settings - named collection of server settings * parameters - arbitrary collection of user-defined parameters * requests - list of requests, one filter string per request, corresponding to a saved search
